Clarence Williams III https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clarence_Williams_III 0 Clarence Williams III (born August 21, 1939) is an American actor. He played the character "Linc Hayes" in the "hippie" cop show The Mod Squad (1968–1973). Clarence_Williams_III ( born August_21_,_1939 ) is an_American_actor .
